---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Triax — Case Study">

  <div class="section">
    <a class="breadcrumb" href="/Personal/case-studies/">← <span>Case Studies</span> / Triax</a>
    <div class="cs-hero">[Triax enterprise content]</div>
    <div class="cs-tags"><span class="cs-tag">B2B SaaS</span><span class="cs-tag">Content</span><span class="cs-tag">Demand Gen</span><span class="cs-tag">Enterprise</span></div>
    <div class="cs-title">B2B SaaS content overhaul for Fortune 50 energy enterprise</div>
    <div class="cs-subtitle">Rewrote the messaging, stood up marketing ops from scratch, and moved Fortune 50 prospects into late-stage pipeline — in five months before a company-wide RIF.</div>
    <div class="cs-meta-card">
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Client</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Triax Technologies</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Duration</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Oct 2021 – Feb 2022</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Role</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Marketing Content Manager</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Industry</div><div class="cs-meta-value">B2B SaaS / IoT</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Prospects</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Hess · Shell</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="stat-strip">
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">300%</div><div class="stat-label">Webinar attendance growth</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">2</div><div class="stat-label">Fortune 50 prospects to late-stage</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">5 mos</div><div class="stat-label">Full marketing ops stood up</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Context · Action · Result</div>
    <div class="car-grid">
      <div class="car-sidebar">
        <div class="car-step active" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-triax-1')"><div class="car-step-label">01 · Context</div><div class="car-step-title">The situation</div></div>
        <div class="car-step" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-triax-2')"><div class="car-step-label">02 · Action</div><div class="car-step-title">What I did</div></div>
        <div class="car-step" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-triax-3')"><div class="car-step-label">03 · Result</div><div class="car-step-title">What it produced</div></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div id="car-triax-1" class="car-content">
          <div class="car-content-label">01 · Context</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">Strong product, broken marketing, stalled pipeline.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">Triax Technologies builds IoT and SaaS solutions for industrial safety and operations. The product was real but the marketing wasn't working. Messaging was written in IoT engineering jargon that the actual buyers — operations and safety leaders at Fortune 500 industrials — couldn't parse. Webinars were pulling 11 attendees. The sales pipeline had stalled. Enterprise prospects like Hess and Shell were aware of the product but weren't moving forward. There was no marketing automation in place — no CRM workflows, no email sequences, no structured content engine.</div>
        </div>
        <div id="car-triax-2" class="car-content" style="display:none">
          <div class="car-content-label">02 · Action</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">Rebuilt messaging, stood up Salesforce and Pardot, and redesigned the webinar program.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">Partnered with the marketing director and sales director to overhaul the content strategy from the ground up. Rewrote all messaging to translate complex SaaS and IoT capabilities into clear business narratives for operational and executive stakeholders. Stood up Salesforce and Pardot for automated email marketing — from zero to operational within the five-month window. Redesigned and executed a webinar series with better content, tighter format, and targeted promotion. Managed two junior marketers executing through Salesforce and social channels.</div>
        </div>
        <div id="car-triax-3" class="car-content" style="display:none">
          <div class="car-content-label">03 · Result</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">300% webinar growth. Two Fortune 50s to late-stage. Marketing ops from zero.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">Webinar attendance grew from 11 to 35 to 55 across three sessions — a 300% increase driven by better content, format, and promotion rather than bigger budgets. Advanced Hess and Shell (both Fortune 50) into late-stage sales conversations through targeted content and strategic messaging. Accelerated a Fortune 500 client through the sales funnel within two months. Implemented Salesforce and Pardot from scratch, giving the company its first real marketing automation capability. A new CEO arrived and laid off roughly a third of the company — marketing, BD, sales, HR. The work stood on its own merit despite the short tenure.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" style="border-bottom:none">
    <hr class="cs-rule" />
    <div class="next-prev">
      <a class="nav-card" href="/Personal/case-studies/kraft-heinz/"><div class="nav-card-dir">← Previous</div><div class="nav-card-title">Kraft Heinz — Digital shelf</div><div class="nav-card-tag">Design · CPG</div></a>
      <a class="nav-card right" href="/Personal/case-studies/infinity/"><div class="nav-card-dir">Next →</div><div class="nav-card-title">Infinity — Licensed CPG</div><div class="nav-card-tag">Brand · Design</div></a>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-row"><a class="btn" href="/Personal/case-studies/">← All case studies</a></div>
  </div>

</Base>
